      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様ー！\nバレンタインライブ、やり切ったよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。月ストのみんなからの告白に\nファンのみんなも大喜びだったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 15.5518369991
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　ドキドキしたけどライブが\n大成功して本当に良かったー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "それでさ、{user}さん\nこの後、二人で話したいんだけど……いいかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 32.077664979
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "構わないが……ライブ後で疲れてたりしないか？\n別に今日じゃなくても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 38.2137416837
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ううん。今日じゃなきゃダメなの\nお願い、そんなに長くならないから……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 41.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。これから少しスタッフさんとの話が\nあるから、現地集合でも大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4708584749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　じゃあ終わったらこの場所に来て！\nそれじゃあまた後でね～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3971.2017692999952,
          "startTime": 58.7045351026
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 58.4545351026
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 58.7045351026
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣から指定された場所に来たはいいが……\nカップルが沢山で浮いてしまってるな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3487352369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、俺と二人で話したいことって\n一体なんなんだ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 71.650997702
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんごめーん！\nミーティングしてたら遅くなっちゃったー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 71.650997702
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だ、そんなに待ってな……め、芽衣！？\nそれ、ライブの衣装じゃないか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7333389283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.7333389283
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 83.912953599
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "えへへー。早く行かないとって焦ってたら\n着替えるの忘れちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.5666722616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "忘れちゃったって、さすがにそれはまずいぞ\n衣装のまま外にいたらすぐに芽衣だとバレて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.7666722616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.1879666326
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ここにいる人達、芽衣のこと\n全然気付いてないみたいだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0000071209,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 97.1879666326
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、本当だ……みんなお互いの恋人ばかり見て……\nカップルの多さに救われたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0000071209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 111.506220849
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、後で着替えに戻らないと……\nこれなら一緒に現場を出た方が良かったかもな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6666737875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 117.912887573
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、そうかも！　でも待ち合わせの方が\nドキドキするって聞いたからさー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.1333404542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 124.7445653913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ドキドキ？　……と、忘れるところだった\n俺に話したいことってなんなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.5666737875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 132.367535877
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "うん、それはね――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.367535877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "はいこれ、チョコレート！\n{user}さんに受け取ってほしいんだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1333404542,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 136.1151741185
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "え……えぇ！？　これって例の本命チョコか！？\nもしかして、芽衣が渡したい相手って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.8333404542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……うん\n{user}さんに渡そうと思ってたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.2000071209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか少し照れちゃうな……\nでも、それって芽衣が本気だからなんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.9333404542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、本気って……え？\nこれ、渡す相手は本当に合っているのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.1666737875,
